name: Forgotten BTC Punks
about:
This collection is a part of sub 10k club.
Once Forgotten, Now Immortalised.
how-to-buy: We handle OTC in the Discord to ensure the safety of buyer and seller, the collection is also available on ordinalswallet and ordswap amongst others.
value-proposiion: FBPs combines the best of the timelessness of Crypto Punks and the !magic of Forgotten Runes Wizard's Cult. The original ETH project has lots going on (several more collections coming, fun on chain mechanisms++), and it will be fun to also see how we can incorporate ordinals into the mix for new and novel ways to innovate in the space.
